    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s super clean, drives smoothly, and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures. I\u2019ve truly loved owning this one, but it\u2019s time for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it feels on the road!",
