    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s example, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional torque vectoring. This chassis has been proactively maintained with documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed trailing arm bushings, preserving the car's legendary handling dynamics. While the exterior displays honest character from spirited use, the mechanical systems are dialed in, offering the sharp throttle response and tactile steering feedback synonymous with the M badge.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
